      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. Uploading/Updating an employee into a gogole sheet with a linked \n2. Check whether this employee information is in the DB\n    2.1 If it is, sent the notification\n    2.2 If it is not, pass inforamtion to OCR/DocumentAI\n3. Pass .md information extracted to an LLM to process all necesary\nsections\n4. Save information into DB\n5. Pass information to the writer and save new output from template",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. Uploading/Updating an employee into a gogole sheet with a linked \n2. Check whether this employee information is in the DB\n    2.1 If it is, sent the notification\n    2.2 If it is not, pass inforamtion to OCR/DocumentAI\n3. Pass .md information extracted to an LLM to process all necesary sections\n4. Save information into DB\n5. Pass information to the writer and save new output from template",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
